{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemail:completion:"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmail:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmail:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmail:completion:"}],"title":"setEmail:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates an email address with the current device with completion confirmation."}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setEmail:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"email","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"email","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The user’s email address. Must be a valid email format."}]}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Same as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setEmail:"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server registration completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Use this when you need to:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Verify email was registered before showing confirmation UI","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Chain operations that depend on email registration","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement error handling and retry logic"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register email during account setup with verification:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class AccountSetupController {","","    func submitEmail(_ email: String) {","        guard isValidEmail(email) else {","            showError(\"Please enter a valid email address\")","            return","        }","","        showLoadingState()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email) { [weak self] error in","            DispatchQueue.main.async {","                self?.hideLoadingState()","","                if let error = error {","                    Logger.error(\"Email registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                    self?.showRetryOption(for: email)","                    return","                }","","                \/\/ Email registered successfully - update tags","                let domain = email.components(separatedBy: \"@\").last ?? \"\"","                Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                    \"has_email\": true,","                    \"email_domain\": domain,","                    \"email_type\": self?.classifyEmailDomain(domain) ?? \"personal\"","                ])","","                self?.proceedToNextStep()","            }","        }","    }","","    private func classifyEmailDomain(_ domain: String) -> String {","        let businessDomains = [\"company.com\", \"enterprise.org\"]","        let educationDomains = [\"edu\", \"ac.uk\", \"edu.au\"]","","        if businessDomains.contains(domain) { return \"business\" }","        if educationDomains.contains(where: { domain.hasSuffix($0) }) { return \"education\" }","        return \"personal\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmail:completion:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmail:completion:":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setEmail:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"setE